-- Assured Guaranty Reassumes $12.9 Billion Portfolio From Radian
-- B y   A n d r e w   F r y e
-- 2012-01-24T22:26:45Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-24/assured-guaranty-reassumes-12-9-billion-portfolio-from-radian.html
Assured Guaranty Ltd. (AGO)  agreed to
reassume a $12.9 billion portfolio of ceded risk tied to public
finance and structured finance credits from  Radian Group Inc. (RDN)   Assured Guaranty will also acquire Municipal and
Infrastructure Assurance Corp. from Radian, Bermuda-based
Assured said today in a statement distributed by Business Wire.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Andrew Frye in New York at 
 afrye@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dan Kraut at   dkraut2@bloomberg.net  